flowchart TD
    A([get_lang called]) --> B{user_data cache<br/>has lang?}
    B -->|Yes| Z([Return cached lang])
    B -->|No| C[get_user from MongoDB]

    C --> D{MongoDB has<br/>lang field?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Store in user_data cache]
    E --> Z
    D -->|No| F{Telegram locale<br/>available?}

    F -->|Yes| G[Take first 2 chars<br/>e.g. ru_RU to ru]
    G --> H{In SUPPORTED_LANGS?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Store in user_data cache]
    I --> Z
    H -->|No| J[Default to en]
    F -->|No| J
    J --> Z

    subgraph Override["/language command override"]
        K([User picks language]) --> L[set_user_language in MongoDB]
        L --> M[set_lang_cache in user_data]
        M --> N[sync_commands BotCommandScopeChat]
        N --> O([Menu localised for this chat])
    end
